{"title":"用​AI​成全抽象​​——首届文心抽象论文大赛正式开启！","slug":"wenxin2604","date":"2026-04-24T16:00:00.975Z","updated":"2026-04-17T04:59:47.507Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/wenxin2604.json","excerpt":"**摘要：**   文心×落碑拾联合举办首届“文心抽象论文大赛”，鼓励参赛者围绕六大荒诞命题（如“舌尖上头实录”“非自我裸奔学”等）创作原创合规的抽象论文，强调基于真实信息、逻辑自洽及公序良俗。投稿需通过百度APP文心助手辅助完成，并附探讨截图，可通过官网或社交媒体（带话题#文心首届抽象论文大赛@百度文心）提交。评审侧重课题抽象性（40%）、论证严谨性（40%）及“胡编感”（30%），顶级作品可豁免标准。设三大奖项：主理人奖（帆布包+智能屏）、总编奖（垃圾桶+迷你屏）、研究员奖（纪念卡+AI鼠标）。获奖作品默认授权主办方发表，无稿酬。活动周期为4月17日-26日，4月24日截止投稿。","covers":["https://img.rubbish.press/file/2604/1776400577569_360901e5f888f8440019593da3899c30.jpg","https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400421903.webp","https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400438973.webp","https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400440208.webp","https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400433076.webp","https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400439975.webp","https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400440538.webp","https://img.rubbish.press/file/2604/1776400958093_image.png","https://img.rubbish.press/file/2604/1776400972743_image.png","https://img.rubbish.press/file/2604/1776400993210_image.png"],"content":"<p>🎉<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>好消息！好消息！用</strong>​<strong>​ AI ​</strong>​<strong>成全抽象</strong></p>\n<p>🏆<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>首届文心抽象论文大赛正式开启！</strong></p>\n<p>​<strong>主办单位</strong>​：文心 × 落碑拾 RUBBISH</p>\n<p>⏰<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>活动时间</strong></p>\n<p>• ​<strong>投稿周期</strong>​：4月17日 - 4月24日</p>\n<p>• ​<strong>获奖公布</strong>​：4月26日</p>\n<h2 id=\"📌​-​​活动要求\">📌<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>活动要求</strong></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>​<strong>抽象课题结论需依据真实可考信息</strong>​（拒绝幻觉从发给我做起）</li>\n<li>使用 <strong>百度</strong>​<strong>​ APP ​</strong>​<strong>文心助手或文心</strong>​<strong>​ APP</strong> 辅助创作。<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.rubbish.press/file/2604/1776400577569_360901e5f888f8440019593da3899c30.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\"></li>\n<li>任选以下命题，突出抽象造诣。</li>\n<li>作品需原创合规、逻辑自洽、符合公序良俗。</li>\n<li>​<strong>字数不限</strong>​。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"🎯​-​​命题范围\">🎯<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>命题范围</strong></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>舌尖上头实录</li>\n<li>铲屎官沦陷范式</li>\n<li>多维关系现场</li>\n<li>非自我裸奔学</li>\n<li>高质量人类的高耗日常</li>\n<li>无可归类实证</li>\n</ol>\n<!-- 6张海报轮播图 HTML 代码开始 -->\n<div style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 24px auto; overflow: hidden;\">\n    <style>\n        .poster-container {\n            width: 100%;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .poster-carousel {\n            display: flex;\n            overflow-x: auto;\n            /* 强制不换行 */\n            flex-wrap: nowrap;\n            /* 丝滑滚动与捕捉 */\n            scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n            /* 隐藏滚动条 */\n            scrollbar-width: none; /* Firefox */\n            -ms-overflow-style: none; /* IE/Edge */\n        }\n        .poster-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar {\n            display: none; /* Chrome, Safari, Opera */\n        }\n        .poster-item {\n            /* 核心修改：flex-grow:0, flex-shrink:0, flex-basis:100% */\n            flex: 0 0 100%; \n            width: 100%;\n            scroll-snap-align: center;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            /* 保持纵横比，防止拉伸 */\n            object-fit: contain;\n            /* 解决图片下方的间隙问题 */\n            display: block;\n        }\n        .carousel-hint {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #888;\n            margin-top: 12px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n    </style>\n<div class=\"poster-container\">\n    <div class=\"poster-carousel\">\n        <img class=\"poster-item\" src=\"https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400421903.webp\" alt=\"命题海报1\">\n        <img class=\"poster-item\" src=\"https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400438973.webp\" alt=\"命题海报2\">\n        <img class=\"poster-item\" src=\"https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400440208.webp\" alt=\"命题海报3\">\n        <img class=\"poster-item\" src=\"https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400433076.webp\" alt=\"命题海报4\">\n        <img class=\"poster-item\" src=\"https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400439975.webp\" alt=\"命题海报5\">\n        <img class=\"poster-item\" src=\"https://pic.knockblog.top/file/2604/1776400440538.webp\" alt=\"命题海报6\">\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- 6张海报轮播图 HTML 代码结束 -->\n<h2 id=\"🚀​-​​投稿渠道\">🚀<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>投稿渠道</strong></h2>\n<p>🔥<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>推荐渠道（官网专属）</strong><br>\n访问 Rubbish 官方网站 <a href=\"https://365.kdocs.cn/wo/sl/v142ELAE\">专属投稿入口</a>，上传文档。</p>\n<p>📱<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>主渠道（社交媒体）</strong><br>\n在 小红书 / 微博 / 抖音 发布投稿，带话题标签 <strong>​#​</strong>​​<strong>文心首届抽象论文大赛</strong>​，并 <strong>​@​</strong>​​<strong>百度文心</strong>​。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>⚠️ <strong>【附件】</strong><br>\n投稿记得附带与百度 APP 文心助手探讨抽象课题的对话截图。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"⚖️​-​​​评审标准​：\">⚖️<strong>​ ​</strong>​​<strong>评审标准</strong>​：</h2>\n<p>• ​<strong>课题抽象性</strong>​：40 分</p>\n<p>• ​<strong>论证严谨性</strong>​：40 分</p>\n<p>• ​<strong>胡编专业论文感</strong>​：30 分</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>💡 ​<strong>PS</strong>​：获评审委员会一致好评的顶级抽象投稿将跳过此标准</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"🎁​-​​奖项设置\">🎁<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>奖项设置</strong></h2>\n<p>🥇<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>​抽象学术研究主理人（​</strong>​<strong>1 ​</strong>​<strong>名）</strong></p>\n<p>• ​<strong>奖品</strong>​：落碑拾帆布包 + 小度智能屏 X10 Ultra</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.rubbish.press/file/2604/1776400958093_image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>🥈<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>​胡编瞎造部总编（​</strong>​<strong>3 ​</strong>​<strong>名）</strong></p>\n<p>• ​<strong>奖品</strong>​：情绪树洞垃圾桶 + 小度智能屏 mini</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.rubbish.press/file/2604/1776400972743_image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>🥉<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>​废话研究员（​</strong>​<strong>5 ​</strong>​<strong>名）</strong></p>\n<p>• ​<strong>奖品</strong>​：Rubbish 已发授权纪念卡 + 文心赋能 AI 智能鼠标</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.rubbish.press/file/2604/1776400993210_image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>📜<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>注意事项</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>获奖名单公布后，官方将及时联系获奖者兑现奖品。</li>\n<li>所有参赛作品默认授权主办方可用于出版物及<em>​ Rubbish ​</em>网站发表，不另支付稿酬。</li>\n</ol>\n","more":"<p>🎉<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>好消息！好消息！用</strong>​<strong>​ AI ​</strong>​<strong>成全抽象</strong></p>\n<p>🏆<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>首届文心抽象论文大赛正式开启！</strong></p>\n<p>​<strong>主办单位</strong>​：文心 × 落碑拾 RUBBISH</p>\n<p>⏰<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>活动时间</strong></p>\n<p>• ​<strong>投稿周期</strong>​：4月17日 - 4月24日</p>\n<p>• ​<strong>获奖公布</strong>​：4月26日</p>\n<h2 id=\"📌​-​​活动要求\">📌<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>活动要求</strong></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>​<strong>抽象课题结论需依据真实可考信息</strong>​（拒绝幻觉从发给我做起）</li>\n<li>使用 <strong>百度</strong>​<strong>​ APP ​</strong>​<strong>文心助手或文心</strong>​<strong>​ APP</strong> 辅助创作。<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.rubbish.press/file/2604/1776400577569_360901e5f888f8440019593da3899c30.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\"></li>\n<li>任选以下命题，突出抽象造诣。</li>\n<li>作品需原创合规、逻辑自洽、符合公序良俗。</li>\n<li>​<strong>字数不限</strong>​。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"🎯​-​​命题范围\">🎯<strong>​ ​</strong>​<strong>命题范围</strong></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>舌尖上头实录</li>\n<li>铲屎官沦陷范式</li>\n<li>多维关系现场</li>\n<li>非自我裸奔学</li>\n<li>高质量人类的高耗日常</li>\n<li>无可归类实证</li>\n</ol>\n<!-- 6张海报轮播图 HTML 代码开始 -->\n<div style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 24px auto; overflow: hidden;\">\n    <style>\n        .poster-container {\n            width: 100%;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .poster-carousel {\n            display: flex;\n            overflow-x: auto;\n            /* 强制不换行 */\n            flex-wrap: nowrap;\n            /* 丝滑滚动与捕捉 */\n            scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n            /* 隐藏滚动条 */\n            scrollbar-width: none; /* Firefox */\n            -ms-overflow-style: none; /* IE/Edge */\n        }\n        .poster-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar {\n            display: none; /* Chrome, Safari, Opera */\n        }\n        .poster-item {\n            /* 核心修改：flex-grow:0, flex-shrink:0, flex-basis:100% */\n            flex: 0 0 100%; \n            